snippet.textDisplay:
Things to discuss about this video:
1.LAUV's VOICE (myghad he never failed to impress me everytime he release a song, I mean who wouldn't love thia guy?
2. JK and Jimin (I mean like... I don't know their voices are so heavenly 😍)
3. The blending of their voices (salute to these three I mean they have their own color but the way they blended it is 😍😍😍)
4. The LYRICS my gosh (it's very deep, I don't have any past relationships but this song is very relatable not only to a bf-gf relationship but also to friendship, that feeling when you don't know who your friend is already)
5. The whole itself (lyrics, voice, production, melody = 10000000000000%)
That's it Thank you
p. s. salute to everyone behind this song, producers, artists, writer etc.
